episodes.title: "You might be in a cult!"
episodes.description:
Rep. Eric Swalwell (D-CA): "My colleagues, none of this today that you are bringing makes sense; your inconsistencies, your hypocrisy, your sycophancy unless you are in a cult. And guys, I'm starting to think you're in a cult." Full video here: https://www.c-span.org/video/?536123-1/attorney-general-testifies-agency-oversight&live
